---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us"
  description="Talk to SnapSkill about AI implementation, corporate training, or the LMS platform. No sales decks, no discovery treadmill — just an honest conversation."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="contact-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="badge">Contact</p>
      <h1>Let's have an honest<br><span class="text-primary">conversation.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">No canned discovery calls. No 30-slide pitch decks. Tell us where you are and what you're trying to do — we'll tell you if and how we can help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact grid -->
  <section class="contact-section section">
    <div class="container contact-inner">

      <!-- Left: channels -->
      <div class="contact-channels">

        <div class="channel-card channel-card--featured">
          <div class="channel-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12 19.79 19.79 0 0 1 1.61 3.43 2 2 0 0 1 3.59 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 8a16 16 0 0 0 7.91 7.91l.72-.72a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Request a callback</h3>
            <p>Book a 30-minute call via Calendly. We'll come prepared with questions — not slides.</p>
            <a href="https://calendly.com/snapskill" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--accent channel-btn">Schedule a call →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="channel-card">
          <div class="channel-icon channel-icon--light" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Email us directly</h3>
            <p>For implementation enquiries, training requests, LMS demos, or anything else.</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@snapskill.in" class="channel-link">support@snapskill.in →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="channel-card">
          <div class="channel-icon channel-icon--light" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Connect on LinkedIn</h3>
            <p>Follow our company page for insights on enterprise AI implementation.</p>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/snapskill" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="channel-link">SnapSkill on LinkedIn →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="response-note">
          <div class="rn-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <p>We typically respond within <strong>one business day</strong>. For urgent implementation queries, email is fastest.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: what to expect -->
      <div class="contact-info">
        <h2>What happens when you reach out</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div>
              <strong>We read everything you send.</strong>
              <p>Every inquiry goes directly to the team. No ticketing system, no auto-response questionnaire.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div>
              <strong>We come prepared.</strong>
              <p>Before the first call, we'll have done our homework on your company, your industry, and your likely AI challenges.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div>
              <strong>We tell you the truth.</strong>
              <p>If your use case isn't ready for AI, we'll say so. If a simpler approach would work, we'll recommend it. We'd rather earn a long-term relationship than a short-term engagement.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">4</div>
            <div>
              <strong>You get a clear next step.</strong>
              <p>No ambiguous follow-up. Every conversation ends with a specific proposal, a defined next action, or an honest "this isn't the right fit."</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-topics">
          <p class="topics-label">Common reasons people reach out</p>
          <div class="topics-grid">
            <div class="topic-chip">AI strategy &amp; roadmap</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">Pilot that's stuck</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">Production implementation</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">Corporate AI training</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">LMS platform demo</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">Data readiness audit</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">Capability building programme</div>
            <div class="topic-chip">Custom enquiry</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .section { padding: var(--space-2xl) 0; }

  /* Hero */
  .contact-hero {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .contact-hero .badge { margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .contact-hero h1 { margin: var(--space-xs) 0 var(--space-sm); }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 540px; }

  /* Layout */
  .contact-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Channels */
  .contact-channels { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md); }

  .channel-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: white;
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .channel-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .channel-card--featured {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    border-color: transparent;
  }
  .channel-card--featured h3 { color: white; }
  .channel-card--featured p  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }

  .channel-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .channel-icon--light { background: rgba(0,123,255,0.1); }

  .channel-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-2xs); }
  .channel-card p  { font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .channel-btn { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .channel-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .channel-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .response-note {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .rn-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #10b981; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(16,185,129,0.2);
  }
  .response-note p { font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0; }

  /* Info side */
  .contact-info h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }

  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .step:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); background: white; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .step-num {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-primary); color: white;
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step strong { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-dark); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .step p { font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0; }

  .contact-topics { }
  .topics-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-body);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .topics-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
  .topic-chip {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0.35em 0.9em;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(0,123,255,0.08);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,123,255,0.2);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .topic-chip:hover { background: var(--color-primary); color: white; cursor: default; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
